 with large scale assembly is also expected in the working area. I am worried for both public safety and public transportation logistics for the day. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nWe appreciate your response by 8PM today (2 August 2019).<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjFtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=06259472\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"4b13a83ef93c92dbe3138217cb95390a9340073c","tid":1396351,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"高登仔=怨婦"},{"pid":"1c9a0cfff4a76eb3dc7f3b9dd02cc1b4a1fa3f98","tid":1396351,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b13a83ef93c92dbe3138217cb95390a9340073c","tid":1396351,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"高登仔=怨婦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:27:07.000Z","msg":"有部分的確係"},{"pid":"58eb3249ec7d8d4dc7993f3788b2f0c35cd9c7fc","tid":1396351,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:28:42.000Z","msg":"屌你啦 咪過左黎 仲想點 引戰狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"